1
00:00:20,622 --> 00:00:23,002
[Dad, Mom,]

2
00:00:24,562 --> 00:00:25,641
[I miss you so much.]

3
00:01:04,462 --> 00:01:05,182
[Zhimei,]

4
00:01:05,801 --> 00:01:06,701
[no matter how busy you are,]

5
00:01:06,942 --> 00:01:08,301
[remember to eat on time.]

6
00:01:15,581 --> 00:01:16,201
[Zhimei,]

7
00:01:16,921 --> 00:01:18,022
[the roses in the yard]

8
00:01:18,542 --> 00:01:20,081
[are blooming beautifully this year.]

9
00:01:20,662 --> 00:01:22,242
[Can you smell their fragrance?]

10
00:01:34,361 --> 00:01:35,221
[Dad,]

11
00:01:35,962 --> 00:01:36,662
[Mom,]

12
00:01:38,141 --> 00:01:39,742
[even if it's fake,]

13
00:01:40,542 --> 00:01:42,721
I really miss you.

14
00:02:07,341 --> 00:02:08,941
I don't know who you are,

15
00:02:10,841 --> 00:02:12,462
but thank you for using this way

16
00:02:13,581 --> 00:02:15,281
to give me back the voice of my parents.

17
00:02:17,381 --> 00:02:20,962
This gift is so precious.

18
00:02:23,781 --> 00:02:24,781
Can I

19
00:02:25,821 --> 00:02:27,561
hear your voice?

20
00:02:28,022 --> 00:02:29,101
Just a little bit.

21
00:02:32,881 --> 00:02:33,522
Hello.

22
00:03:20,962 --> 00:03:21,802
Don't scare me anymore.

23
00:03:22,402 --> 00:03:23,841
I can't take it

24
00:03:24,761 --> 00:03:26,061
if I lose you again.

25
00:03:31,441 --> 00:03:32,182
Honey,

26
00:03:36,402 --> 00:03:37,041
the medicine

27
00:03:37,821 --> 00:03:38,541
makes me

28
00:03:39,302 --> 00:03:41,182
feel dizzy all the time.

29
00:03:41,441 --> 00:03:43,221
I can't see you clearly.

30
00:03:43,922 --> 00:03:44,561
I won't take it anymore,

31
00:03:45,402 --> 00:03:46,242
okay?

32
00:03:53,622 --> 00:03:54,702
Then take care.

33
00:03:55,781 --> 00:03:57,501
Don't torture yourself

34
00:03:58,142 --> 00:03:59,622
with unrealistic thoughts,

35
00:04:00,242 --> 00:04:01,082
and me,

36
00:04:02,161 --> 00:04:02,802
okay?

37
00:04:12,422 --> 00:04:13,061
Okay.

38
00:05:13,381 --> 00:05:14,441
Not yet.

39
00:05:15,242 --> 00:05:16,001
What's wrong?

40
00:05:17,602 --> 00:05:19,542
Are you mad at me

41
00:05:20,602 --> 00:05:22,021
because I don't recognize you?

42
00:05:25,802 --> 00:05:27,602
Don't be so distant,

43
00:05:28,602 --> 00:05:29,422
okay?

44
00:05:42,182 --> 00:05:42,881
Don't be silly.

45
00:05:43,482 --> 00:05:45,581
The doctor said you need rest.

46
00:05:46,362 --> 00:05:47,342
Let's talk when you're well.

47
00:05:48,102 --> 00:05:49,521
I'll go back to work.

48
00:05:51,381 --> 00:05:52,282
Honey.

49
00:05:52,662 --> 00:05:53,742
Honey.

50
00:05:58,901 --> 00:06:01,441
If not for lust, then for money.

51
00:06:02,682 --> 00:06:05,901
Wu Xi's death must be related to him.

52
00:06:06,982 --> 00:06:07,302
Sir,

53
00:06:08,061 --> 00:06:09,242
the surveillance on the mountain road

54
00:06:09,242 --> 00:06:11,242
has been confirmed to be deliberately damaged.

55
00:06:11,641 --> 00:06:12,842
The other party is very professional,

56
00:06:13,242 --> 00:06:14,362
leaving no traces behind.

57
00:06:19,001 --> 00:06:19,922
Not a single clue?

58
00:06:22,102 --> 00:06:22,941
No.

59
00:06:26,581 --> 00:06:27,662
No matter what method is used,

60
00:06:28,162 --> 00:06:29,761
you must find the person for me.

61
00:06:30,001 --> 00:06:30,682
Yes, sir.

62
00:06:50,821 --> 00:06:51,441
Who is it?

63
00:06:52,362 --> 00:06:52,901
You scared me.

64
00:06:53,362 --> 00:06:54,961
A delivery from the Shiguang Florist.

65
00:06:55,302 --> 00:06:56,081
Why is it delivered by someone else?

66
00:06:56,641 --> 00:06:57,961
Let me check what you're carrying.

67
00:06:58,561 --> 00:06:59,782
Living in a big villa, so what?

68
00:06:59,802 --> 00:07:00,941
Why so many rules?

69
00:07:01,021 --> 00:07:01,881
Bring it here for me to check.

70
00:07:02,682 --> 00:07:03,782
This is Louis XVI.

71
00:07:03,782 --> 00:07:04,602
If you break it, you'll have to pay for it.

72
00:07:04,602 --> 00:07:05,581
Give it to me. I'll check it.

73
00:07:05,602 --> 00:07:06,342
No.

74
00:07:07,362 --> 00:07:08,021
Give it to me.

75
00:07:08,362 --> 00:07:09,182
Stop.

76
00:07:14,042 --> 00:07:15,102
Don't be so rude to a girl.

77
00:07:15,682 --> 00:07:16,102
Yes.

78
00:07:16,321 --> 00:07:16,742
Go away.

79
00:07:19,622 --> 00:07:21,162
I don't know what's wrong with my roses.

80
00:07:21,362 --> 00:07:22,441
Can you help me check them?

81
00:07:23,722 --> 00:07:24,941
I'm professional at taking care of roses.

82
00:07:25,482 --> 00:07:26,321
Where are they?

83
00:07:27,102 --> 00:07:28,021
Just follow me.

84
00:07:33,001 --> 00:07:33,542
Wait.

85
00:07:36,701 --> 00:07:37,321
Honey,

86
00:07:45,342 --> 00:07:46,802
I've hired a gardener for tomorrow.

87
00:07:47,261 --> 00:07:48,521
He's a top expert in the industry.

88
00:07:49,302 --> 00:07:51,061
These flowers are a memory of my parents.

89
00:07:51,641 --> 00:07:52,561
I'm not comfortable

90
00:07:53,261 --> 00:07:54,162
leaving them with a stranger.

91
00:07:57,162 --> 00:07:57,802
Sorry.

92
00:07:58,182 --> 00:08:00,061
My husband is very thoughtful.

93
00:08:00,561 --> 00:08:01,482
Fine.

94
00:08:01,941 --> 00:08:02,561
Then,

95
00:08:02,561 --> 00:08:04,901
you must take good care of these roses.

96
00:08:05,302 --> 00:08:06,662
They are quite delicate,

97
00:08:07,381 --> 00:08:09,622
They need ventilation

98
00:08:09,821 --> 00:08:10,722
after 10 pm,

99
00:08:10,881 --> 00:08:11,802
or the roots will rot.

100
00:08:11,922 --> 00:08:12,162
Okay.

101
00:08:13,982 --> 00:08:15,342
Call me if you have any questions.

102
00:08:15,521 --> 00:08:16,261
I'm always...

103
00:08:22,042 --> 00:08:23,482
When the night dew moistens,

104
00:08:23,641 --> 00:08:24,501
loosen soil for morning light.

105
00:08:24,881 --> 00:08:26,461
My original flower care mantra.

106
00:08:38,201 --> 00:08:38,961
Thank you.

107
00:08:39,342 --> 00:08:40,702
I know what to do now.

108
00:08:43,021 --> 00:08:43,842
I'm off.

109
00:08:44,021 --> 00:08:45,381
My next order is about to be overdue.

110
00:09:01,622 --> 00:09:02,301
[Jiayi.]

111
00:09:06,202 --> 00:09:06,862
Meimei.

112
00:09:07,062 --> 00:09:08,362
I finally got in touch with you.

113
00:09:09,881 --> 00:09:12,141
You've been completely off the grid these past few months.

114
00:09:14,122 --> 00:09:15,141
How have you been

115
00:09:15,161 --> 00:09:16,442
these days?

116
00:09:17,102 --> 00:09:18,401
I even found out someone

117
00:09:18,401 --> 00:09:19,521
put up a high bounty

118
00:09:20,001 --> 00:09:21,381
on a dark web

119
00:09:21,401 --> 00:09:22,982
to hire someone to hurt you.

120
00:09:23,482 --> 00:09:24,161
Hire someone?

121
00:09:28,041 --> 00:09:29,501
[So the diving accident and the car crash]

122
00:09:29,921 --> 00:09:30,881
[were both man-made.]

123
00:09:34,181 --> 00:09:34,702
[Meimei,]

124
00:09:35,342 --> 00:09:37,041
[who is that man by your side?]

125
00:09:37,602 --> 00:09:40,641
[He looks very dangerous.]

126
00:09:41,401 --> 00:09:42,281
[I really don't know.]

127
00:09:43,842 --> 00:09:44,862
[But]

128
00:09:45,462 --> 00:09:47,021
[he must have something to do]

129
00:09:47,842 --> 00:09:49,141
[with my husband's death.]

130
00:09:52,082 --> 00:09:52,602
[Jiayi,]

131
00:09:53,342 --> 00:09:54,462
[you are the person I trust the most.]

132
00:09:55,342 --> 00:09:56,342
[I need your help.]

133
00:09:56,722 --> 00:09:57,602
[Who's there?]

134
00:10:04,661 --> 00:10:05,381
Honey,

135
00:10:07,722 --> 00:10:08,342
it's me.

136
00:10:09,082 --> 00:10:10,442
I thought there was something wrong

137
00:10:10,462 --> 00:10:11,342
with the roses my parents planted,

138
00:10:12,322 --> 00:10:13,362
so I came to check.

139
00:10:15,722 --> 00:10:16,661
Silly girl.

140
00:10:16,822 --> 00:10:17,781
How could that be?

141
00:10:19,301 --> 00:10:19,822
As long as I'm here,

142
00:10:21,301 --> 00:10:22,822
everything you cherish

143
00:10:23,781 --> 00:10:24,842
will remain intact.

144
00:10:27,482 --> 00:10:28,041
And you

145
00:10:28,681 --> 00:10:31,021
will stay in the garden I built for you forever.

146
00:11:09,001 --> 00:11:09,921
Honey,

147
00:11:11,141 --> 00:11:12,141
I'm cold.

148
00:11:32,842 --> 00:11:34,562
Let's go back to the room.
